### Get data
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolio/report?tickers=AAPL:0.5,MSFT:0.5&riskFreeRate=0.0

### Create
POST http://localhost:5138/portfolios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Test Portfolio",
  "tickerWeights": { "AAPL": 0.5, "MSFT": 0.5 }
}

### List
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolios

### Get by id (replace 1 with the id returned above)
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolios/2

### Delete
DELETE http://localhost:5138/portfolios/1

### Confirm delete (should 404)
GET http://localhost:5138/portfolios/2